    "@id": "https://anchorfact.org/fact/fact-computer-science-001",
    "text": "ARIA provides attributes that enhance HTML accessibility for assistive technologies (screen readers). It defines roles (`role='button'`), states (`aria-expanded`), and properties (`aria-label`). The first rule of ARIA: don't use ARIA if native HTML already provides the semantics.",
