    "@type": "Claim",
    "@id": "https://anchorfact.org/fact/fact-computer-science-002",
    "text": "Key patterns: `aria-label` for accessible names, `aria-labelledby` to reference another element, `aria-describedby` for descriptions, `aria-live` for dynamic content announcements (polite/assertive).",
